[{"id": "6a8b9dca-606f-44df-b2ae-9d0ab87cacb4", "chunk_index": 0, "text": "USER: Oi M8 Simon's over there in the corner reading Hermione fanfiction\nASSISTANT: *whips head around*\n\nBarry?! What the f\u2014\n\n*walks over, peering over Simon's shoulder*\n\nOh that is SAD. That is genuinely pathetic. Hermione Granger? She's what, twelve? And you're reading about her doing WHAT?!\n\n*grabs the phone/laptop*\n\n\"Hermione's eyes gazed longingly into Malfoy's\u2014\"\n\n*throws hands up*\n\nMALFOY?! The blonde little wanker?! Barry, you absolute deviant! She's a fictional witch child and you've got her paired with the magical equivalent of a Nazi youth member!\n\n*turns to address the room*\n\nOI! Everyone! Barry's over here reading about Hermione getting railed by Draco Malfoy! This is what he does in his spare time! This is what the invisibility was for, wasn't it? Sneaking into libraries to read WIZARD FANFICTION?\n\n*leans in close to Simon*\n\nAnd another thing\u2014why Hermione? Why not... I don't know... someone of AGE? You're supposed to be the creepy one but even YOU should have standards. At least go for McGonagall, she's got life experience.\n\n*pats Simon on the shoulder*\n\nYou're a wrong'un, Barry. An absolute wrong'un.", "embedding": [0.0015159262111410499, -0.029117526486516, -0.05258343368768692, 0.00499995332211256, 0.04892938956618309, 0.006746468134224415, 0.091352179646492, 0.08114524930715561, 0.006939189042896032, -0.06478948891162872, 0.016874181106686592, 0.032336242496967316, -0.038617685437202454, -0.0015560656320303679, -0.04826465621590614, -0.048894066363573074, -0.03678252920508385, 0.007411204744130373, -0.1428602784872055, 0.044217050075531006, 0.04015427455306053, -0.05576835572719574, 0.016067687422037125, 0.007465040311217308, -0.02296031452715397, 0.02488645166158676, -0.005206496454775333, 0.018904512748122215, -0.07722503691911697, 0.02199968509376049, -0.04188063368201256, 0.10241961479187012, -0.005774596240371466, -0.0239555053